# Design rules

- The approved design system lives in docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md. Until Phase 3 completes,
  make no final visual decisions.
- Working concept: "Mobilna klima laboratorija na točkovima" — technical precision,
  cold air, mobility, local trust, modern premium look.
- The hero must impress immediately ("wow" on first view) — owner's explicit requirement.
  Never ship a generic auto-service template (car photo + blue button + three cards).
- Forbidden: generic snowflake illustrations, excessive neon, stock luxury car photos,
  animating every element, large blocking hero video, fake statistics or reviews,
  text over important parts of photos.
- Real photos of the technician and equipment are placeholders for now — every image
  placeholder must describe what the real photo should show (see docs/CLIENT_DATA.md).
- Asymmetric layout, generous whitespace, clear visual hierarchy, strong CTAs.
- Mobile-first: the same key offer, text and CTAs must exist on mobile.
